Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever they decide, Apple\NBloom, we'll be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it could\Nchange everything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forever! And ever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We here have decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're old enough\Nto stay home alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and take care of the chores\Nyourself for the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying home alone!\NWhoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By myself! On my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm\Nreally doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hey there, filly.\NI know you're excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But bein' the only pony here to\Ntake care of the day's chores
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is a big responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And it means everything\Nto me that ya'll think
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grown up enough\Nto handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if'n I'm gonna make\Nmy train, I best to be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When Great-Aunt Pine Apple\Nsays a pony's gots to arrive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,by a certain time, you\Nbetter be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You be sure and take\Ncare now, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all take care as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know which of your\Ndelivery routes is tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're each headed to a{\i0}\N{\i1}mighty hard-to-reach town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We know, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason I\Nagreed to let Apple Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}stay behind alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't mean it\Nlike that, Sugar Cube.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I take my job as\Nyour big sister real serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I spent\Nall night making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little list\Nof helpful reminders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's some soup for\Nyou in the fridgerator."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Be sure not to heat\Nit up too much."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"If its hot, blow on\Nit to cool it off."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"And take little sips;"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"if you gulp, you\Ncould get hiccups."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nworry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take of myself\Nand the chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not so sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you trust me and believe I'm\Ngrown up enough to handle this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, little sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,OK great!\Nsee you soon. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye! So long!{\i0}\N{\i1}See ya! Bye now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be so AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Big Mac.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just frettin' a\Nbit about Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she's gonna\Nbe OK on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep on thinking\Nof things I forgot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to put on her list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I didn't write down that\Nif she wants to get a spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the drawer, she needs\Nto open the drawer first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm probably\Njust being silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I'd feel a heap\Nbetter if I could just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,check on Apple Bloom\None last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead and\Nmake your delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna take quick\Npeek and then I'll make mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OK, number 172.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Make sure to pump the bellows\Nto keep the stove warm."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Make sure the Hats and Bows\Ncloset is fully stocked."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's everything\Non Applejack's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that my chores are done,\Nsince there's no one else here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to make all the decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I want to listen\Nto music, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I want to read a book, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wanna just stand here in\Nthe kitchen talking to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!\NApple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back to check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am so glad I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought about how\Ndangerous things are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. But I'm\Nreally gonna be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm here,\Nand I'm staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way am I leaving\Nmy little baby sister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,home alone all by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about those pies\Nyou're supposed to deliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pies? Ha. Family's way\Nmore important than pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And actually, this was\Nkind of your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I should never have\Nleft you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't need you\Nlooking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly capable\Nof staying home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's some soup for you\Nin the fridgerator."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is worse than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here now and I'm not leaving\Nyou home alone ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sticking right\Nby your side, always!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack's just\Nover reactin' a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you mean well, but I\Ndon't need you watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care\Nof things myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who put pillows\Non this rake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone who really\Nloves her little sister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and doesn't want her\Nto get an owie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Applejack, watch me buck\Nthese apples on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without anything bad\Nhappening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! For the love of...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone and\Nbaby-proofed everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big sister\Nlet you down once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I promise it won't\Never happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you\Nwatching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, that's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you trying\Nto make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry; I'll\NALWAYS be here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason I asked\Ny'all to come over quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Apple Bloom,{\i0}\N{\i1}you need anything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A snack? A hoof massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a snack while\Nhavin' a hoof massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that sounds delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, well, you can count\Non me being close by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, I'm never\Ngoing to be able to do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,without Applejack\Nhoverin' over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sneak out\Nand deliver them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny said they were going
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to some incredibly\Nhard-to-reach town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can do it alone,\Nthat'll show Applejack
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need somepony\Nwatchin' over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one problem: your\Nsister's gonna come back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and check on you any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you\Nneed an escape plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! And I got\Nan idea for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It'll look just like\Nyou're sleeping in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie and I can take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, when one of us gets\Ntired, the other can take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a feelin' this\Njust might work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We're gonna make my{\i0}\N{\i1}sister see ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I don't need her{\i0}\N{\i1}watchin' over me! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No time for a song!\NApplejack's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to go, we've\Ngot to get you out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cutie Mark Crusaders!{\i0}\N{\i1}Let's do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything all right{\i0}\N{\i1}in there, Sugar Cube?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Get in while I hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie, No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta sleep\Nlike Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How does she sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Like she does\Neverything. With sass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you must've\Nbeen so tuckered out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you sent your friends\Nhome and went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, you are\Na delicate flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep tight, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check on you\Nagain in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just checking in on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Need anything now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Need another blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hear a cough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just checkin' in on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you, dozin'\Nso peaceful-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, checkin' up on ya\Nevery five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't need me\Nfrettin' over you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Apple Bloom will be\Nso glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could be anywhere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She could be lost, cold,{\i0}\N{\i1}hungry, itchy, stuffed up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}needin' to go to the bathroom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We know\Nexactly where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's making\Nyour pie delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't she hear how difficult\Nand dangerous it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I may never see my\Nlittle sister again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Rarity's on her way here\Nto look after you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell me, did Apple Bloom at\Nleast bring flame-proof boots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A lion tamer's chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake-charming flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A hunk of ricotta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's still time to\Ncatch her before she gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did she leave?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a darn\Nthing in this swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now at least I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only safe\Nspot around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It don't look\Nso safe to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we just mean\Nfrom the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you guys sssspeak up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to tell our guest\Nhow we haven't eaten in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My sisters and I can never\Nagree on what to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Except pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, unfortunately, I got to\Nget these pies to a town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}on the other side of{\i0}\N{\i1}the swamp. So uh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't have\Nto worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't have to\Nworry about anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're gonna\Nhave our apple pie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with a sssside\Nof filly filet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now sisters, on three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the pies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you've always\Ngot to be in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got no idea what it's\Nlike to have a sister
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}constantly looking{\i0}\N{\i1}over your shoulder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try listening\Nto me for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say: if\Nthere are no pies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let's settle for\Nthe filly filet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wish my\Nsister were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang on, Apple Bloom!{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm a'comin'!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I\Nwas in charge now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm. Ricotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya ya need your big\Nsister looking after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad this\Nwasn't a whole lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, sure, we lost the\Ncart and all the pies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but at least you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The cart! And all the pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually got them all\Nthe up way here, in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,through the Flame Geyser\NSwamp, past that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That's mighty\Nimpressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anypony who can do\Nthat on her own, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she don't need somepony\Nlike me babying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm!\NAndouille!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dis pie's even tastier den ma\Nmama's swamp-water casserole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, now, Mama,\Ndon't be like dat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember, you fellas\Nwouldn't be enjoyin' these pies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if it weren't for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And MY sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But this don't change the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that trying to make this\Ndelivery on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was a plumb crazy\Nthing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Granny Smith grounds you\Nfor a month for sneakin' out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Big Mac, Granny Smith\Nand I ever have to be away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for the day again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would totally trust\Nyou to stay home
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and take care of\Nthings on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I did get a little\Ncarried away watchin' over ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and if ya hadn't snuck\Nout like you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I wouldn't have\Nfigured that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now that is the kind\Nof looking out for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can definitely appreciate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Little sister,\Nwe're always good.
